  notes:
    - "This spec extends inspect_extra118.zspec.zsdl."
    - "This spec covers: inspect.Attribute namedtuple class attributes not yet covered — Attribute._fields element access ([0]='name', [1]='kind', [2]='defining_class', [3]='object'), Attribute._fields element string lengths ([0]=4, [1]=4, [2]=14, [3]=6), Attribute._make.__qualname__ ('Attribute._make', len 15), Attribute._asdict.__qualname__ ('Attribute._asdict', len 17), Attribute.__mro__.__len__ (3); wave 270."
    - "inspect.Attribute._fields[0] == 'name'. Verified with Python 3.14.3."
    - "inspect.Attribute._fields[1] == 'kind'. Verified with Python 3.14.3."
    - "inspect.Attribute._fields[2] == 'defining_class'. Verified with Python 3.14.3."
    - "inspect.Attribute._fields[3] == 'object'. Verified with Python 3.14.3."
